data.description: Motivated Seller! Make an offer today! Meticulously maintained, one owner 3 BR 2 Bath with Flex Room & Pocket Office. Home has a wonderful open concept with granite countertops, and eat in kitchen. The Living Area comes with a gas  fireplace for cozy night entertaining. Home also has a pocket office or bar area, an entertainers choice. Flex room can be used as an office, etc. Two car garage with lots of attic storage. Energy star SS Appliances and soft lighting throughout home. Primary bedroom is located in rear of home for privacy. Primary bath comes with separate soaking tub and WI shower and a large WI closet. Both secondary rooms are very spacious with large closets. This home has a wonderful curb appeal and is located within walking distance of doe branch park which has a public boat dock. Amenities include multiple community centers, multiple pools, H&B trails and playgrounds for the young ones. Perfect location of Little Elm with access to many restaurants and shopping centers.
